WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.520 --> 00:00:05.700
You, my dear, can you say goodbye?

2
00:00:10.480 --> 00:00:14.120
Why are you ignoring me? I will be your mother from now on?

3
00:00:23.500 --> 00:00:25.200
You said you were too disappointed with your mother, are you coming back again? What?

4
00:00:25.200 --> 00:00:27.040
Hello, yes, mom is here?

5
00:00:27.620 --> 00:00:30.360
Why are you back?

6
00:00:30.360 --> 00:00:31.560
Are you still a child?

7
00:00:31.600 --> 00:00:34.780
How could you arrest him? Why do you have to talk to me like this?

8
00:00:35.290 --> 00:00:37.290
You are just looking out for the protection of my family.

9
00:00:38.230 --> 00:00:40.990
As for Ali, Gu Yue, have you called City Half?

10
00:00:41.590 --> 00:00:43.210
I want to marry the city,

11
00:00:43.470 --> 00:00:45.160
Then he calls me mother for life,

12
00:00:45.160 --> 00:00:45.360
What's wrong?

13
00:00:47.160 --> 00:00:49.000
Dad, Dad, please ask my room

14
00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:54.520
I will no longer call you mom

15
00:00:54.520 --> 00:00:56.340
I will make you hurt again

16
00:00:57.520 --> 00:00:58.480
Mr. sister-in-law

17
00:00:58.480 --> 00:01:00.800
What shoes are you holding on to?

18
00:01:02.730 --> 00:01:04.180
How about not letting your children recognize anyone other than you?

19
00:01:04.780 --> 00:01:07.040
Thought you were Yue, your biological mother

20
00:01:07.040 --> 00:01:08.980
It is my deep love for her that I love you

21
00:01:08.980 --> 00:01:11.200
I just want to be in the position where I hurt myself.

22
00:01:11.200 --> 00:01:13.500
You haven't seen your own identity either

23
00:01:14.670 --> 00:01:15.930
Fuck you

24
00:01:17.290 --> 00:01:21.260
Don't make any mistakes, otherwise

25
00:01:21.260 --> 00:01:22.820
Wait until Chen and I get married

26
00:01:22.820 --> 00:01:24.200
your own children

27
00:01:24.670 --> 00:01:26.350
This little testimony of yours

28
00:01:30.850 --> 00:01:31.670
Can you have a good life? Xiao Siqin

29
00:01:32.190 --> 00:01:33.990
Mom doesn’t want this

30
00:01:36.890 --> 00:01:38.090
I don’t know who I gave birth to, and the little one testifies that life is hard.

31
00:01:38.270 --> 00:01:39.450
You'd better take him with you

32
00:01:41.650 --> 00:01:42.590
Li Chen is a member of the Gu family, or else

33
00:01:42.740 --> 00:01:44.060
Unsure of the day he will be born

34
00:01:44.060 --> 00:01:45.280
He can't do it anymore

